s|TAG_BIO_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Bipasha Basu Opposite Hollywood Star Billy Zane</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bipasha Basu Opposite Hollywood Star Billy Zane" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/06_01_2009.html">06/07/2009</A>: <br> Director Tapan Saha has signed Titanic star Billy Zane opposite <A ALT="" TITLE="Bipasha Basu" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/bipasha_basu/bollywood_bipasha_basu.html">Bipasha Basu</A> in his upcoming movie <A ALT="" TITLE="Chimera Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/movie_reviews/2009/chimera.html">Chimera (2009)</A> . The director has also promised a passionate scene between Billy and Bipasha. Shabana Azmi will play Bipasha’s mother, and <A ALT="" TITLE="Anil Kapoor" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/anil_kapoor/bollywood_anil_kapoor.html">Anil Kapoor</A> as Zane’s Indian friend. Earlier Bipasha has done love scenes opposite <A ALT="" TITLE="Saif Ali Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/saif_ali_khan/bollywood_saif_ali_khan.html">Saif Ali Khan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="John Abraham" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/john_abraham/bollywood_john_abraham.html">John Abraham</A> .<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Aishwarya Rai Bachchan And Sonam Kapoor To Walk On Red Carpet Cannes</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan And Sonam Kapoor To Walk On Red Carpet Cannes" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/05_11_2009.html">05/12/2009</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Sonam Kapoor" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/sonam_kapoor/bollywood_sonam_kapoor.html">Sonam Kapoor</A> will walk the red carpet at the Cannes film international film festival along side <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai (Aishwarya Bachchan)" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> , Hollywood beauties <A ALT="" TITLE="Penelope Cruz" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/celebrites/penelope_cruz/celebrites_penelope_cruz.html">Penelope Cruz</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Eva Longoria Parker" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/actress/eva_longoria/hollywood_eva_longoria.html">Eva Longoria</A> as the face of a major international cosmetic giant. Sonam will be joined by her dad <A ALT="" TITLE="Anil Kapoor" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/anil_kapoor/bollywood_anil_kapoor.html">Anil Kapoor</A> , who is basking in the sun from the the Oscars and Golden Globes winning movie <A ALT="" TITLE="Slumdog Millionaire (Crorepati) Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2008/slumdog_millionaire.html">Slumdog Millionaire (Crorepati) (2008)</A> .<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Slumdog Millionaire Get 10 Oscar Nominations</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Slumdog Millionaire Get 10 Oscar Nominations" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/01_19_2009.html">01/22/2009</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Slumdog Millionaire Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2008/slumdog_millionaire.html">Slumdog Millionaire (2008)</A> received 10 Oscar nominations. The movie has become a world wide phenomenon and is due to release in India tomorrow January 23, 2009. It has already picked up four Golden Globe for Best Screenplay, <A ALT="" TITLE="AR Rahman" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/music_director/ar_rahman/bollywood_ar_rahman_filmography.html">AR Rahman</A> for Best Original Score, Best Director Dale Boyle and Best Movie. Its Oscar nominations are for Best Picture, Best Director, Best Adapted Screenplay, Best Cinematography, Best Film Editing, Best Original Score, Best Original Song (2 nominations for O...Saya and Jai Ho), Best Sound Editing, and Best Sound Mixing. <BR> The film stars <A ALT="" TITLE="Dev Patel" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/dev_patel/bollywood_dev_patel.html">Dev Patel</A>, <A ALT="" TITLE="Anil Kapoor" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/anil_kapoor/bollywood_anil_kapoor.html">Anil Kapoor</A>, and <A ALT="" TITLE="Freida Pinto" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/freida_pinto/bollywood_freida_pinto.html">Freida Pinto</A> and is directed by Danny Boyle.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Slumdog Millionaire Wins 4 Golden Globes</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Slumdog Millionaire Wins 4 Golden Globes" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/01_12_2009.html">01/11/2009</A>: <br> It started with winning the Screenplay awards for <A ALT="" TITLE="Slumdog Millionaire Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2008/slumdog_millionaire.html">Slumdog Millionaire (2008)</A> by Simon Beaufoy followed by the mistro himself, <A ALT="" TITLE="AR Rahman" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/music_director/ar_rahman/bollywood_ar_rahman_filmography.html">AR Rahman</A> for Best Original Score. Then the man who put it all together, the director Dale Boyle and they closed out the night by winning the best movie drama. The film stars <A ALT="" TITLE="Dev Patel" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/dev_patel/bollywood_dev_patel.html">Dev Patel</A>, <A ALT="" TITLE="Anil Kapoor" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/anil_kapoor/bollywood_anil_kapoor.html">Anil Kapoor</A>, and <A ALT="" TITLE="Freida Pinto" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/freida_pinto/bollywood_freida_pinto.html">Freida Pinto</A> and is directed by Danny Boyle. The movie will release all over India on January 23, 2009.|g
